Here are paste-ready photorealistic prompts you can use in Nano Banana (or similar image models). Pick one scene or mix details from two prompts.

Construction
Prompt:
Photorealistic mid-rise building shell under construction, rebar and concrete decks with yellow guardrails, tower crane boom angled across a partly cloudy sky, workers in hard hats and harnesses at a perimeter edge (small scale, safety-first), mortar pans and stacked forms in foreground, dust and diesel haze backlit, 24–70mm site documentary framing, believable PPE wear and mud on boots, no readable jobsite banners, no developer logos, no faces toward camera.

Shot on full-frame DSLR, 85mm or 35mm, f/5.6–f/8 for clarity, Adobe neutral profile, minimal oversharpening, natural chromatic aberration, real-world imperfections, documentary editorial style.


